65
00:05:13,920 --> 00:05:18,142
My first challenge was to find out what is Remedy's character pipeline.

66
00:05:19,364 --> 00:05:23,988
By pipeline, I address the collection of methods of the different sections of the process

67
00:05:24,529 --> 00:05:28,533
and the professionals who are involved with the visualisation of the characters.

68
00:05:29,414 --> 00:05:36,562
