193
00:17:46,776 --> 00:17:49,237
These in-character photos were further utilized

194
00:17:49,397 --> 00:17:50,238
in concept art.

195
00:17:53,521 --> 00:17:55,342
Based on the photo shoot's costume tests,

196
00:17:55,642 --> 00:17:58,184
I defined the final outfit on the left.

